headline: Otis (NYSE:OTIS) Misses Q4 CY2025 Sales Expectations
summary: Elevator manufacturer Otis (NYSE:OTIS) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025 as sales rose 3.3% year on year to $3.80 billion. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $15.15 billion at the midpoint came in 0.7% below analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.03 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.
